msgid "This backup was created on another router or by an older Sheepfold version. Device numbers, groups, schedules and lists will be kept, but device fingerprints and administrator phone bindings will be rebuilt. Pair administrator phones again after import."
msgstr "此备份来自另一台路由器或较旧版本的 Sheepfold。设备编号、分组、时间表和列表会保留，但设备指纹及管理员手机绑定将重新建立。导入后请重新配对管理员手机。"

